- Zarkali A et al. (2025) Mov Disord 40(11):2367-2380. [DOI](https://doi.org/10.1002/mds.30325) [Only QSM + DTI-ALPS combined study; PD: lower ALPS associated with iron distribution changes]
- Hsu JL et al. (2023) Ann Neurol 93(1):164-174. [DOI](https://doi.org/10.1002/ana.26516) [ALPS mediates between amyloid/tau PET and cognitive dysfunction in AD]
