| Valacyclovir | Antiviral                            | Prevention works, treatment fails | Fragment model: can't clear existing debris                                         | Consistent        |
| VZV vaccine  | Prevention                           | ~20% dementia reduction           | Prevents new fragment deposition                                                    | Consistent        |
| DMF/DRF      | Nrf2 activator                       | MS approved                       | Anti-ferroptotic via GPX4 upregulation                                              | Consistent        |
| Fingolimod   | S1PR modulator                       | MS approved                       | May protect BBB, indirect E layer effect                                            | PARTIAL           |

